{"tid":465064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正常廁所客滿，究竟可唔可以用冇人使殘廁","createTime":"2017-11-11T07:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T10:17:38.000Z","uid":116211,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5764051dd069e2f16df961d7cd7f4630c3981e","tid":465064,"uid":116211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:22:48.000Z","msg":"商場去男廁開大，冇哂坐廁<br />\n等左陣，都冇位，好急出返去見到個殘廁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇人使用</span></span>即刻邊入邊解皮帶<br />\n好舒𣈱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人喪拍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為又有巴打有需要<br />\n就速戰速決啦<br />\n一開門有個4眼阿嬸，一個輪椅使用者，一個賓賓企係門口怒啤小弟<br />\n4眼阿嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先生你知殘廁係比殘障人士用果可？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知，男廁滿左呢到又冇人先去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解你唔去男廁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我去過滿左先去呢到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你冇！點解你個正常人要同有需要既人搶廁所<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男廁入面得2個坐廁都滿左，我係入面出黎，見冇人用先用姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見住你入殘廁冇入男廁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點會冇阿！入面2個坐廁都有人用緊阿，我肯定！入去睇阿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你用心諗下受咁多年教育咁做岩唔岩啦(轉身入殘廁)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾時開始用殘廁同關愛座一樣要受批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 小弟正正常常，冇任何殘障殘疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e64d8f57a278456ee7ab5961d6d70e0e8ec977","tid":465064,"uid":1895,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"同佢講你腦殘就得啦 腦殘唔撚係殘呀？<br />\n利申：成日去殘廁開大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ba19b5b9332acfb82b862cc5ccca043731895f","tid":465064,"uid":22227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"138ec5773d73aa6c01188b4d50a534a57c622543","tid":465064,"uid":79036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"急屎理得佢老母姓咩"},{"pid":"4a669578bcabc67ca205989d94bc19fd6b22dc0e","tid":465064,"uid":47029,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:34:19.000Z","msg":"搶佢老母咩，你殘障排緊我見到唔撚讓你就話啫，冇人用都唔撚俾用都直頭反撚智"},{"pid":"d0746a48282dff862b6e3cce16bb77a7c9464848","tid":465064,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:35:05.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通賴起地下咩"},{"pid":"5d09fa9958c275ac9906ea63c1b5caf232122b02","tid":465064,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"殘廁開大最撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地方大，有廁紙，仲要冇咁臭"},{"pid":"c832398188bf23b4c2f0437b5c6159644c31ec26","tid":465064,"uid":15309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"仲講咁多 係我直接走啦"},{"pid":"8e4b360ab43d3dfcedaa90d6d4b7e937e83a01a0","tid":465064,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b8f1d68c343ad8bc48aaee6dfcd0b9e8b18cf91","tid":465064,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"馬上扮腦殘<br />\n流撚哂口水<br />\n睇佢咩反應"},{"pid":"e7daa227ad0727a6da2801c3892724cbf9a13