ji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ec4d8ce5d4a280019e4c5c6b689dda0140e444","tid":465064,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:24:41.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢咩 都認左低威解釋左男廁冇位啦 仲想點 急起上嚟有乜計 唔通瀨咩"},{"pid":"734115d41be916fd54acc8588b540b463e640358","tid":465064,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢啦"},{"pid":"ca4f6be32536aadd16257c276ea0e0a255f233bd","tid":465064,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>商場去男廁開大，冇哂坐廁<br />\n等左陣，都冇位，好急出返去見到個殘廁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇人使用</span></span>即刻邊入邊解皮帶<br />\n好舒𣈱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人喪拍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為又有巴打有需要<br />\n就速戰速決啦<br />\n一開門有個4眼阿嬸，一個輪椅使用者，一個賓賓企係門口怒啤小弟<br />\n4眼阿嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先生你知殘廁係比殘障人士用果可？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知，男廁滿左呢到又冇人先去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解你唔去男廁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我去過滿左先去呢到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你冇！點解你個正常人要同有需要既人搶廁所<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男廁入面得2個坐廁都滿左，我係入面出黎，見冇人用先用姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見住你入殘廁冇入男廁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點會冇阿！入面2個坐廁都有人用緊阿，我肯定！入去睇阿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你用心諗下受咁多年教育咁做岩唔岩啦(轉身入殘廁)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑人問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾時開始用殘廁同關愛座一樣要受批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 小弟正正常常，冇任何殘障殘疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自認自稱腦殘就用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab0db452669b7670a898009d6ae8af608cce672","tid":465064,"uid":33809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:45:43.000Z","msg":"係你先咁on9同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbang門走理撚得佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7256dcdc3c5524a27c591be5e520941e368f41c","tid":465064,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"殘廁只係殘疾人士優使用，一般人都用得。"},{"pid":"3300365b54d32da5dc20d4b40ab7f841bd1ed17a","tid":465064,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"扮聾扮啞咪得囉"},{"pid":"90d2efad433de770cd0483ad1b460f4d9df0f5b3","tid":465064,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"屎急到爆拎個膠袋屙都得啦, 何況只係入殘廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}